For installation see 'INSTALL'
Under development files are given in 'under_dev_files'[Useful for developers]

To remove a feature from calculator permanently change 'calc_features.h' file.

For example if you want to get rid of colors/fonts from the calculator
permanently then remove or comment out '#define CALC_COLORS' from
'calc_features.h' header file and compile the program[See INSTALL for
compilation].